ActCanada Infrastructure Bank Act
PrecisAppointment of JANE BIRD of Vancouver, British Columbia, to be Chairperson of the board of directors of the Canada Infrastructure Bank, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year or until such time as a new Chaiperson is appointed, whichever occurs first.
